  kreativitas.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:&#10;  27.0pt;line-height:115%"><sup><span lang="IN" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;  line-height:115%">5</span></sup><span lang="IN" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;  line-height:115%">Penelitian menunjukkan bahwa berpikir kreatif melibatkan
