  settlements on Madagascar, home to about 22 million people today.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;  115%"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%">          Genetic
